General Information

Each Splenda tablet has the same sweetness as a teaspoon of sugar (5g), without all the calories.

Common Uses

Use Splenda low calorie sweetener tablets to sweeten tea or coffee

Ingredients

Lactose (from milk) sweetener (sucralose) 40%, croscarmellose sodium, l-leucine, magnesium stearate

Directions

one splenda tablet is equivalent to 1 level teaspoon of sugar
